## Container Usage

The CLI is available as a container image:

```bash
# Pull the image
docker pull ghcr.io/metaschema-framework/oscal-cli:latest

# Run with mounted volume
docker run --rm -v "$(pwd):/data" ghcr.io/metaschema-framework/oscal-cli:latest \
    validate /data/document.json
```

See the [Installation](installation.html) guide for CI/CD integration examples.

## Shell Completion

Enable tab completion for Bash or Zsh:

```bash
# Bash
oscal-cli generate-completion bash > ~/.local/share/bash-completion/completions/oscal-cli

# Zsh
oscal-cli generate-completion zsh > ~/.zsh/completions/_oscal-cli
```

